# Data — standard D&D reference catalogs
# NOTE: spell/monster bodies are copied wholesale. Keep their commentary campaign-neutral
# in the source repo before syncing — do not let campaign proper nouns (NPC names, place
# names, module names) leak into these reference files, or they ship into the template.
